g.ns0:text: \\center{Each crossing of the link becomes an edge in the corresponding \\\\\nblink, the graph whose vertices are distinguished points placed at the\\\\\ninterior of the gray faces and in 1-1 correspondence with these \\\\\nin a bicoloration of the faces of the diagram into white and gray.\n}
\\center{The thick edge of the blink is\\\\\ngray if the upper strand is from\\\\\n northwest to southeast}
\\center{The thick edge of the blink is \\\\\nblack if the upper strand is from\\\\\n northeast to southwest}
